People's Daily commentator: "The 14th Five-Year Plan" has a good start - On studying and implementing the spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference - Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, December 11th.
People's Daily, December 12th commentator's article: "The 14th Five-Year Plan" has a good start - On studying and implementing the spirit of the Central Economic Work Conference.
"Achieving a good start of the 14th Five-Year Plan," the Central Economic Work Conference held from December 8th to 10th highly evaluated the achievements of China's economic and social development in the past year.
General Secretary Xi Jinping delivered important speeches at the conference, deeply summarizing the 2021 economic work and analyzing the current economic situation. He made major deployments for the 2022 economic work and prepared for next year's economic work, and welcomed the successful convening of the Party's 20th Congress, pointing out the direction for progress and providing fundamental guidance.
We celebrate the 100th anniversary of the founding of the Communist Party of China and officially announce the comprehensive achievement of a moderately prosperous society and the realization of the first centenary goal, opening a new journey towards the comprehensive construction of a socialist modernized country and the second centenary goal.
We held the 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, summarized the great achievements and historical experiences of the Party's hundred-year struggle, and passed the third historical resolution in the history of the hundred-year Party history, "The Resolution of the Communist Party of China Central Committee on the Great Achievements and Historical Experience of the Party's Hundred-Year Struggle." This is a political declaration for the new era Communist Party of China to remember its original mission and purpose, to adhere to and develop Chinese socialism, and to be a guide for looking back at history, creating the future, and realizing the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
In the past year, the world has undergone a hundred-year unprecedented change and the global outbreak of the novel coronavirus pandemic, and the external environment has become more complicated and severe. The task of controlling the novel coronavirus epidemic and developing the economy and society is extremely heavy and arduous.
With Comrade Xi Jinping as the core, the Party Central Committee has adhered to the overall management of both domestic and international affairs, adhered to the general tone of stability, progress, and seeking progress in work, calmly responded to the hundred-year change and the century-old epidemic, coordinated epidemic prevention and control with economic and social development, accelerated the construction of a new development pattern, strengthened cross-cycle adjustment of macro policies, and made efforts to promote sustained and healthy economic development, deepen reform and opening up, and innovation, and strive to complete the arduous tasks of reform and development. The Party and the state have achieved new major achievements in various undertakings.
The "14th Five-Year Plan" achieved a good start, which was reflected in a significant aspect that the construction of a new development pattern took a new step and high-quality development achieved new results.
Our country's economic development and epidemic prevention and control maintain a global leading position, and the characteristics of strong resilience, great potential, and sufficient momentum continue to be revealed. The national strategic technological strength is accelerating its growth, and major innovative results are emerging one after another, and technological innovation capacity continues to improve, and new breakthroughs have been made in key core technologies. The resilience of the industrial chain has been improved, the volume and quality of foreign trade has increased, the structure has continued to be optimized, and new dynamic forces represented by new industries, new forms, and new models have grown and become stronger. Reform and opening up are being pushed forward in depth, efforts are being made to break through the bottlenecks that restrict supply and demand adaptation and factor flow, and high-level opening-up is creating new advantages for cooperation and competition. The people's livelihood is effectively guaranteed, the scale of employment continues to expand, the growth of residents' income is basically in sync with economic growth, food output has remained above 130 billion jin for seven consecutive years, and the "18 consecutive bumper harvests" have been achieved. The construction of ecological civilization continues to advance, carbon peak and carbon neutral work is coordinated and pushed forward, the pace of green and low-carbon transformation is steady and steady, and new achievements have been made in ecological environment protection.
The attainment of these achievements is the result of the strong leadership of the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping as the core. It is the result of the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping's thoughts on socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era. It is the result of the concerted and arduous efforts of all party members and all ethnic groups throughout the country.
Practice has once again proved that establishing Comrade Xi Jinping as the core of the Party Central Committee and the whole party, and establishing the guiding position of Xi Jinping's thoughts on socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era, has a decisive significance for the development of the Party and the state, and for advancing the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
With General Secretary Xi Jinping as the core of the Party Central Committee and the whole party, with the scientific guidance of Xi Jinping's thoughts on socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era, and with the unity and persistent efforts of all party members and all ethnic groups throughout the country, we will surely overcome all difficulties and create new epochal brilliance and new historical feats in the new journey of building a modern socialist country in an all-round way.
Next year, the Party's 20th congress will be held, which is a major event in the political life of the Party and the state.
We will carry forward the great spirit of founding the Party, persist in the general principle of seeking progress while ensuring stability, implement the new development concept in a comprehensive, accurate and full manner, speed up the construction of a new development pattern, deepen reform and opening up in an all-round way, and drive development through innovation. We will promote high-quality development, prioritize supply-side structural reform, coordinate epidemic prevention and control with economic and social development, coordinate development and security, continue to do a good job of "six stability" and "six guarantees," improve people's livelihoods, strive to stabilize the macro economy, maintain a reasonable range of economic operation, maintain social stability, and we will certainly maintain a stable and healthy economic environment, a peaceful and prosperous social environment, and a clean and upright political environment, and welcome the success of the 20th congress of the Party with outstanding achievements.
Let us unite more closely around the Party Central Committee with Comrade Xi Jinping as the core, enhance the "four consciousnesses," firm up the "four self-confidences," achieve the "two maintenance," continuously improve our political judgement, political understanding, and political execution, implement the decisions and deployments of the Party Central Committee in practical actions, and continuously push the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era forward.